HEADWORD: Bramble bush
<hw>Bram"ble bush`</hw> <pr>(b⟦usdot⟧sh`)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The bramble, or a collection of brambles growing
together.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He jumped into a <qex>bramble bush</qex>⟦br⟧
